
 Interceptor
 ~~~~~~~~~~~

F1-F10   Thrust in 10% increments.  After F9, hit F10 twice for afterburners.
=        Thrust +
-        Thrust -
]        Zoom in.
[        Zoom out.
BACKSPCE Brakes.
RETURN   Weapon select.
SPACE    Fire weapon.
ENTER    Toggle inside view/outside view.
SHIFT-F  Release rescue pod.  (Some missions.)
SHIFT-E  Eject.
ESC      Reset mission.
SHFT-ESC Main menu.
,        Left rudder.
.        Right rudder.
A        Arrestor hook activate. (For carrier landing.)
C        Chaff release.
F        Flare release.
G        Gear up/down.
H        HUD diaplay toggle.
K        Radar jam.
M        Map.
P        Pause
R        Radar range.
T        Target toggle.

Use cursor keys to control plane, numeric keypad to control view.

